{"tid":59403,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"樂視英超播放權暫至1月3日","createTime":"2016-12-29T15:14:04.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-29T15:34:39.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"201e3eebbc57731346cf6d8a808d7fef2d8517ac","tid":59403,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T15:14:04.000Z","msg":"【樂視英超播放權暫至1月3日】<br />\n<br />\n有用戶發現樂視體育在 26 日的英超比賽直播，到下半場時訊號中斷，令人懷疑樂視能否繼續轉播賽事。<br />\n<br />\n擁有英超轉播權的新英體育指，當晚沒有暫停給樂視的播放訊號，但該公司透露，和樂視已達成新的還款備忘。<br />\n<br />\n目前樂視所支付的版權費尾數，只足夠把播放權延續到 1 月 3 日，之後能否繼續將會成為疑問。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2F&d=HJ3VHFVOi4atUZKNgWQtTGN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=9b9acdd8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/</a>"},{"pid":"bcc75a783bad9996c8332ed50b19bec47e2d3ebe","tid":59403,"uid":1643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T15:28:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04238160dc3c4b92e082c4719d1e616f1f0deecf","tid":59403,"uid":9170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T15:29:15.000Z","msg":"呢個好似係講支那?"},{"pid":"e3473de5d69c9c978918040f397eeb29d42f9f3a","tid":59403,"uid":581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T15:34:39.000Z","msg":"淨係支那"}]}